Title: KAVANA — Deep Work, Delivered
Credit: Group biu-int3 | AI Course Ex06
Author: biu-int3
Draft date: 2026-06-23

====

INT. DIGITAL WORKSPACE — DAY

A clean navy screen. Particles drift slowly.

ON SCREEN TEXT:
Your focus is under attack.

VOICEOVER
Every ping steals a piece of your day.

====

INT. CHAOTIC DESKTOP — CONTINUOUS

Notification cards SLAM in from every edge — Slack, Gmail, Calendar, Teams — each card pulsing with a red urgency dot.

A horizontal FOCUS METER at center drains: 100%... 67%... 34%... 12%. The bar turns crimson.

Calendar blocks on the right SHATTER into tiny fragments, scattering like broken glass.

ON SCREEN TEXT:
47 interruptions. Before lunch.

VOICEOVER
Forty-seven interruptions before lunch. Your calendar looks like shattered glass.

====

INT. KAVANA ACTIVATION — CONTINUOUS

The noise FREEZES mid-air. A luminous shield icon expands from center — concentric rings of violet and cyan.

Notification cards DISSOLVE into soft particles that fade downward.

The focus meter REVERSES — climbing back: 12%... 45%... 78%... 94%.

ON SCREEN TEXT:
Kavana
AI Deep-Work Companion

VOICEOVER
Meet Kavana. Your AI deep-work companion.

====

INT. FEATURE SHOWCASE — CONTINUOUS

Three feature panels slide in sequentially:

PANEL 1 — A bell icon with a slash through it. Label: "Focus Shield"
PANEL 2 — Calendar blocks auto-snap into clean rows. Label: "Smart Orchestration"
PANEL 3 — Single priority card glows at center. Label: "Clarity Dashboard"

ON SCREEN TEXT:
Shield. Orchestrate. Clarify.

VOICEOVER
Shield your focus. Orchestrate your day. One priority at a time.

====

INT. RESULTS DASHBOARD — CONTINUOUS

Split-screen animation:

LEFT (Before): "2.1 hrs deep work" in red, declining arrow.
RIGHT (After): "5.8 hrs deep work" in green, rising arrow.

A counter ticks up: "+176% focus time"

ON SCREEN TEXT:
+176% deep work time

VOICEOVER
Users report nearly triple the deep-work hours. Less noise. More done.

====

INT. CALL TO ACTION — CONTINUOUS

Kavana logo centers on screen — a stylized shield with the letter K.

Tagline fades in below in English, then Hebrew beneath.

ON SCREEN TEXT:
Start your focused day.
kavana.ai

HEBREW TEXT (RTL):
כוונה אחת. יום שלם.

VOICEOVER
Start your focused day. Kavana — one intention, a whole day.

FADE OUT.

====

END
